00:02:04,614 --> 00:02:42,102
1. Stream FIFO DUT (shared course RTL). Course DUT: common_dut/rtl/stream_fifo.sv — parameterizable DEPTH and DATA_WIDTH. Source interface: s_valid, s_ready, s_data (push when both valid and ready). Sink interface: m_valid, m_ready, m_data (pop on handshake). Internal storage: circular buffer (mem, wr_ptr, rd_ptr, count). Refer to the diagram on the right.

11
