2. Planning-level verification view (Module 1). No full UVM implementation required yet — document intended env boundaries in VERIFICATION_PLAN.md. REQUIREMENTS_MATRIX.md traces features → future tests and coverage bins. common_dut/tb/ holds skeleton stubs so architecture decisions are concrete, not abstract. Refer to the diagram on the right.

